data.description: Gorgeous 5 bed, 3.5 bath featuring dual master suites in the desirable Weston Oaks community. Open concept floor plan. Kitchen boasts dark mocha cabinets, gas cooking, granite counter tops, tile back-splash, and stainless steel appliances. Relax in your downstairs master oasis complete with a sitting room, tray ceiling, separate  garden tub and shower, and large walk-in closet. Enjoy your backyard under a covered patio looking out over mature trees providing ample shade on hot Texas days.
